{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"&nbsp;","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7450,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491791456000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"问：为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>答：因为看书好无聊，如果玩游戏就不难坚持了。</div><div>问：为什么会觉得看书无聊？</div><div>答：因为大部分书是专业类或提升能力、开拓思维的类别的，需要精力集中，深入思考。比起玩游戏，看书是主动学习的过程，不是享受，会比较辛苦。</div><div>问：既然能增长知识、提升能力，为什么还无法忍受辛苦？</div><div>答：因为很多时候看书（尤其是专业书）没有明确的目的，知识点零散，不成系统，也不利于以后的应用。这样就会觉得看书没什么用，枯燥又耗费精力，没有成就感，很容易放弃。</div><div>问：有时候我们抱着目的去看书，为什么也不容易坚持下去？</div><div>答：因为有目的我们会有针对性地看书，更有效。但有时为了解决某个问题，需要看大量的书，如果不设计有效的反馈机制，也容易放弃。可以考虑：经常把看过的东西应用于工作生活中；给自己一点小奖励，等等会更有效。</div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7425,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491729807000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"因为他没有兴趣啊！为什么没有兴趣啊！它枯燥乏味！解决枯燥无味就能提高坚持每天看书的习惯。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7311,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491529190000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lasia","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPZjdCpPKAMDUgWoXUvkVcsqzWKUUicQdLDqSSXIAzKphVGZMibQL8RZHItR7wlTetH47SYQgiasgxu/0","content":"<p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">1.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>因为就上班族而言，工作一天已经很累了。下班后只想休闲娱乐下，比如刷刷手机、看看剧等。</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>为什么大家愿意花时间刷手机、看剧，而不愿意花时间学习呢？</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>因为刷手机、看剧属于被动接受行为，不用动脑，而学习属于需要学习者参与进去的主动行为，需要动脑。</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">3.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>为什么被动接受行为比主动参与学习的行为更易被大家接受？</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>因为从儿童入学开始，我们接受的几乎都是老师被动传授的知识，这种方式为大家接受、习得后对此种方式习以为常。而主动参与的学习行为虽然已被广为倡导，但很多人都处于</font>“只知其名而不知其道”的地位。因此当他们看书学习，却难以看到相应收益时，就会对看书学习失去兴趣和信心，进而放弃。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7288,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491469890000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"若雨","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6KqxbZia6ia3HF8IalMbc2wl4E1GTVgrOv3TD6kD92XbeyKPDNH668v5v7O45WMJiaYgHSGib6hiaPocagd/0","content":"<p>1.为什么不每天看书？</p><p>因为不喜欢看书。</p><p>2.为什么不喜欢看书？</p><p>因为看书没用。</p><p>3.为什么觉得看书没用？</p><p>对自己的工作发展和个人提升没有帮助。</p><p>4. 如果看书对自己的工作<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">发展和个人提升</span>没有帮助，那你怎样实现自己的工作发展和个人提升呢？</p><p>不需要个人提升，工作发展。现在这样就蛮好的。</p><p>总结：如果这样来提问的话，我认为大多数人不坚持每天看书的主要原因是<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">认为看书对自己没有用</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">，没有看书的意愿，。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7271,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491450085000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>为什么很难坚持每天看书？</p><p>因为没有时间用来看书。</p><p>为什么<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">没有时间用来看书？</span></p><p>因为工作时间忙，下班后忙家务，陪孩子。有点时间，就想放松一会。</p><p>为什么图书不能让人放松？</p><p>因为虚构类的书籍容易沉浸其中，占用太多休息时间。非虚构的书籍太耗脑力而且容易有挫败感。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">为什么非虚构的书籍太耗脑力而且容易有挫败感？</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">之前积累有限，学习新东西比较吃力，总是对自己很失望。认为自己就这样了，根本不会通过读书得到成长。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">为半途而废的次数太多了，没有过成功的体验。不相信自己能坚持读书。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;为什么不相信自己能坚持读书？</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">因为遭遇挫折时总是自我怀疑和自我批评。要面对自己的挫折，学着原谅自己，以避免罪恶感让自己放弃。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7186,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491302688000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"彭兄","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XrFctaWMO6Hek8JfFDOtEWYnA1pDX3hqjFlmjKDCFj3jID1iaMsXedtNka7iaBAcWnQiaZCCzKlMFyQ/0","content":"<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">从这个题目来看，应该分析的是原计划看书的人（有兴趣或愿望或利益驱动）没有坚持下去的原因，因此应该排除掉那些本来就不爱看书的人不经常看书的情况和少部分学神学霸有良好阅读习惯的情况。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span>原因可能是：<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">遇到一些计划外的情况，影响了看书的时间，从而打断了每天看书的计划。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why看书时间受到影响，就会中断每天看书的计划？这一天太累了，没有心情没有精力看书，不如明天再看吧。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why太累会影响看书的心情和精力？因为看书任务压力大，造成了拖延的心理。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why看书任务压力大？不看书就是不够进取有为，就是懒惰无能，引发了自己的焦虑。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why看书和进取有为联系在一起？因为看书的目的性太强，太注重结果，没有享受看书的乐趣。</span></span></p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7113,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491148998000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Atia文晨","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLB0Y2Nsibnz5eWwDJAOhMbEEbKMjQn9X8mj3icwQXoEP4xzmw1h85Miba2YMmcKSv42eFNTGXI0icWtfA/0","content":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px !important;\">1.因为大多数人会把是时间花在太多其他事情上，没有合理分配时间</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">因为很多人不懂得缺乏有效的时间管理知识</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">因为学校没有教授相关知识，而且大多数人也比较缺乏时间管理意识</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7111,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491144424000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"丁一鸣\uD83C\uDF3E","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-01","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM4vrefdoqnO2s5EthQOch2icOLgAMWGzN1u3RTa0jF61gc7DiabdIQ8NVMBJw520t41neAicNqEaMzCQ/0","content":"为什么大家很难坚持看书？因为坚持很难。为什么坚持很难？因为外界诱惑多，无法抵挡。为什么无法抵挡？因为内心不安定，想要的太多。为什么想要得太多了？因为没有明白把一件事做好就是做好的道理。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7078,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491053846000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"李冰雅","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-01","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bJV4Niaky3XicMLYDv7VAJGBz0FhcgUrlnypwHWKLmEt0DFAD4XM1UibknGUuGdWVYYx1JeMexDclp3TgricvcJy9v/0","content":"因为大家没有形成看书的习惯<div>为什么没有形成看书的习惯？</div><div>因为大家没有规划出每天的专门用来看书的时间来培养习惯。</div><div>为什么不规划？</div><div>因为不了解看书的重要性，对看书没有兴趣，或者没有这类时间，或者没有利用这类时间来看书</div><div>为什么没有利用这类时间？</div><div>因为每天下班也比较累了，想看看电视放松一下</div><div>为什么看电视比看书放松？</div><div>因为不需要过多的思考。</div><div>为什么不喜欢思考？</div><div>没有感受的思考的乐趣和没有了解到思考的重要性。</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7059,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491009142000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"慢慢","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCibt7FJPfX3NmQXJgwib4vSzH4KZYdazV7mVIb2T19rMp17IOWPFRtUtw3EGtywx9BBGozp9Lacl6w/0","content":"1、为什么很难坚持每天看书？\n因为没时间，很忙。\n2、为什么会没时间？\n因为工作任务重，回家又很累，所以不愿意看书\n3、为什么会工作任务重却没时间看书？为什么回家之后也不愿意看书？工作任务重表示挑战大，更应该看书学习啊。\n因为工作总在做一些重复性的东西，所以不需要学习更多的东西，回家后没有动力看书。\n4、为什么总在做一些重复性的工作？\n总是被动地接一些重复性的工作，自己也地时间分配也不合理\n5、为什么总是被动接受重复性工作，并且时间分配不合理？\n自己能力不足，领导经常安排重复性工作给我，由于自己不去分析每项工作的重要程度，导致在重复的工作上花费时间太多，没有发展一些有优势的地方，所以领导不交代太复杂的工作给我。\n6、为什么不去分析工作的重要程度？\n因为对未来没有规划，没有提升的方向。\n7、那么接下来该怎么做？\n找到自己需要提升的方向，有计划地做工作，不重要的事情迅速完成，在有挑战的工作上多花时间，做出成果，让领导看到自己的特点，今后少分配重复性工作给我，并通过看书来学习，了解自己并提升自己的能力。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7002,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490961415000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"晓露sheri","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyxPrKibibicpRzMx57Dib8I3mv4PIzcBzYNV8PZ3rMsjPExB3icliaYpuJL3KGBMEdqaAEPKN83ayRcnibO/0","content":"1.坚持的困难点在哪？\n没有持续的热情.\n2、为什么没有持续的热情？\n没有归属感.\n3、怎么样提供归属感？\n学以致用，得到喜悦。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6950,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490943064000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"元气少女\uD83C\uDF3B","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-30","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEtZxnzBwbLAzpTXp5C3ZzUHD4DU6cvkh8OklJNSCZ8mXDhbEV4AggLvNYTNhvP5NdpIVt1D4iajHk/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？\n因为看书很枯燥\n为什么大多数人觉得看书很枯燥？\n因为现代生活吸收知识越来越容易，而看书是最枯燥的一种，且需要静心下来看，并且要读懂才能获得感悟或者知识，让人无法坚持。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6838,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490887721000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"新悦","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKuPUVAWGIRxAVo4SkNmEc9bGP9bCibGTSef90ZbzXj36qdNpqdrRH6LOJCquviaiaicVoqk7bwsJm8RqNY3dwRkjiaC/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？\n因为很多人没有养成习惯\n为什么大多数人无法养成看书的习惯？\n因为没有时间\n为什么没有时间？因为没有规划安排\n为什么没有规划安排？因为执行力差比较懒惰","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6617,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490803014000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浅紫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5Qias5Y6BOJq0bibrmkolNJFtbyicK1y9rN41JY4SIw04awshr8lhByygakZc9SVzOfPej1XNTbShq/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？\n因为没有规划，并执行，成为习惯？\n为什么没有规划，执行，并成为习惯？\n因为变化太多，而且没有掌握自己生活的规律\n为什么没有掌握自己生活的规律就执行不了看书成为习惯？\n因为如果一个人一天都很忙，那规划每天早起半小时，看书，并长期执行成习惯，那问题就解决了\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6413,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490714524000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"零五七","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLrFd5bPVEw4BRmkPkP5sMhsygdDwvgHiaWISQXnIXqBeHRX9uOIiciaRwETN4FxUeO0ktPBBBORFgmC37DFAUkJd0/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？因为大多数人没有养成每天看书的习惯。为什么没有养成每天看书的习惯？因为看书的时间不固定就不能养成习惯。为什么看书的时间不固定就不能养成每天看书的习惯？为什么要有固定的时间看书才能养成每天看书的习惯？因为我们每天都做的事情都是在固定的时间去完成的，比方说起床，洗漱，通勤，吃饭，睡眠。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6359,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490702891000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jill Ling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyyZN53g2CvLEGicxZ4heLHooiaCVwibvbcw8BcDsxgL2AMj3bgU2wNX8OPexCoDeHxKxE9KicExhXd1G/0","content":"1 。 为什么很难坚持每天看书？ 因为每天都会有很多计划外的事情打断事先的安排\n2。  为什么可以坚持每天刷牙洗脸？因为花的时间少，而且养成了习惯\n3。  MM每天化妆的时间也不少啊，为什么可以坚持每天化妆？因为花妆比较重要\n4。  看书也很重要啊，为什么坚持不了呢？因为化妆可以立刻看到效果，而化妆不行\n5。  为什么看书不能立刻见到效果呢？ 因为看书没有即时的输出。\n\n所以如果要做到每天坚持看书，比较好的方法是：\n1。养成习惯\n2。及时输出，比如与朋友分享读书心得，或者用书中的方法去解决问题","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6299,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490680850000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张YY","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLDC88nCjl5mticEwn6d95CyLS2K9XiaEIPB6n8icXpxKiaNZlVIVbTBj7XJVOQvkuoOHDzbycbc5YU9tA/0","content":"问：为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书\n\n答：因为没有更多空余的时间。\n\n问：为什么会没有那多的空余时间看书呢？\n\n答：因为城市越来越大，上班路上所花费的时间很多；此外每天人们要忙很多事情，如工作，加班，带孩子，聚会，逛街等\n\n问：那为什么不能乘坐公共交通工具，在路上看书呢？\n\n因为注意力很难集中，很难静下心来每天看书。\n    \n\n由于外界的干扰太多，不能静下心来读书，很难形成习惯。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5639,"type":11,"voteStat